{"tid":2312522,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳李嘉誠外甥查毅超初步確診 科技園須全面消毒","createTime":"2020-12-05T04:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T05:52:43.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"852f1859c096e8b5fdfe5781d7f5fdbec09a2a5e","tid":2312522,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:39:01.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎第4波疫情繼續惡化，最新香港科技園公司董事局證實，其中一位董事局成員初步確診，目前正接受進一步測試。有傳這位成員為香港科技園公司董事局主席查毅超，他是李嘉誠外甥，也有「磅秤大王」之稱，現時是福田集團董事總經理，以生產圍繞秤重相關產品為主。<br />\n<br />\n科技園指，初步確診董事成員最近一次到訪科技園為12月2日星期三，科技園管理團隊表明已即時為相關辦公室、會議室、走廊等設計進行消毒，並已在今日完成相關消毒工作。<br />\n<br />\n科技園亦指示園區內的科技公司，可考慮讓員工留家工作，或時刻提醒員工在工作場所戴上口罩，以及進入工作大樓前測量體溫，如發現員工有任何病徵或確診，請即通知科技園管理公司。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201205/C5BAFGTZBFCVRIUGDPHXBNUCFI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201205%2FC5BAFGTZBFCVRIUGDPHXBNUCFI%2F&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1wywbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=c24a8da1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201205%2FC5BAFGTZBFCVRIUGDPHXBNUCFI%2F&h=f6967e40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201205/C5BAFGTZBFCVRIUGDPHXBNUCFI/</a>"},{"pid":"b8244bac1fdab2e2a0274e9118553ed9e89ce6c4","tid":2312522,"uid":123591,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:40:31.000Z","msg":"呢隻病毒真係好鍾意有錢佬真識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d24a614b44415ece9668282c9969f99545d5df","tid":2312522,"uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b8244bac1fdab2e2a0274e9118553ed9e89ce6c4","tid":2312522,"uid":123591,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:40:31.000Z","msg":"呢隻病毒真係好鍾意有錢佬真識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:41:36.000Z","msg":"我識袁國勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f960be5333b5e64451bafd32d47680